==English==
===Noun===
'''cinder'''  (plural ''[[cinders]]'')
# [[partially]] or [[completely]] [[burnt]] [[material]] that [[result]]s from a [[fire]] of [[coal]] or [[wood]] etc; [[clinker]]
# [[slag]] from a [[metal]] [[furnace]]

